      "created_at": "2024-06-07T10:20:38.802Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Is it possible for you to take my fit files from wahoo systm, that performs a steady 10,20,30,40 kmh and extrapolate/interpolate(?) the generated watts from the app?</p>\n<p>I\u2019m really wanting this work, or maybe you could let us add a custom trainer powercurve so we can tweak it from there? Because mag trainer is usually linear, so it should be close to the app</p>",
