      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/57b2e6/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2024-06-07T10:33:09.899Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Follow these instructions and send the results back to <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/alex\">@Alex</a> to add it to the curves:</p>\n<aside class=\"quote quote-modified\" data-post=\"69\" data-topic=\"211\">\n  <div class=\"title\">\n    <div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/57b2e6/48.png\" class=\"avatar\">\n    <a href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/t/i-would-like-virtual-power-will-you-add-it-completed/211/69\">I would like virtual power. Will you add it? (COMPLETED)</a> <a class=\"badge-category__wrapper \" href=\"/c/feature-requests/requests-completed/18\"><span data-category-id=\"18\" style=\"--category-badge-color: #0088CC; --category-badge-text-color: #FFFFFF; --parent-category-badge-color: #0088CC;\" data-parent-category-id=\"13\" data-drop-close=\"true\" class=\"badge-category --has-parent\" title=\"These are items that we have completed\"><span class=\"badge-category__name\">Completed</span></span></a>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n    In attachment the picture with the power/speed curve that I used to derive the formula for the Elite Arion Mag. Can\u2019t attach the Excel file used for the calculation. \n\nOpen the picture with an image viewer that shows pixel coordinates (GIMP, Irfan View,\u2026)\nZoom in on the picture and determine the intercept of X and Y axis. Enter the coordinates on the first tab of the Excel file\nFind 2 well determined speed values and enter their value and coordinates. In this case there were no vertical raster l\u2026\n  </blockquote>\n</aside>\n",
